# Carpenter Python

Python backend module for [CarpenterJS](https://github.com/erickweyunga/CarpenterJS) â€“ enabling server-side actions with a clean interface and developer-first tooling.

## Features

- Register and handle server actions
- Plug into existing frameworks (FastAPI, Starlette)
- Simple CLI for bootstrapping apps

## Installation

```bash
pip install carpenter
